# OS-level: nghttp2 in python:3.11-slim-bookworm base image.
# Fix not yet available in Debian bookworm repos. Nanobot does not use
# nghttp2 directly; it is pulled in as a transitive dependency of libcurl.
# Will be resolved when the base image publishes an updated package.
CVE-2026-27135  # nghttp2 in base image, no fix available — reviewed 2026-03-20
